## <a id="mysql-certs"></a> Certificates Used by <%= vars.product_short %>

If you are using <%= vars.ops_manager %> v2.9 or later, you can rotate all MySQL
certificates in the table below using CredHub Maestro.
For <%= vars.ops_manager %> v2.9 and earlier, you can rotate the Services TLS CA
using a manual procedure.
For more information about procedures to use to rotate certificates, see
[Rotate Services TLS Certificate Authority](#tls) above.


